                </h2>
                <div
                  id="collapseFour"
                  class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                  data-bs-parent="#accordionExample"
                >
                  <div class="accordion-body">
                    <p>
                      Payment is sent to you through Mobile Money after
                      successful completion of a tutorial assignment.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <!-- FIFTH FAQ TUTOR -->
              <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                  <button
                    class="accordion-button collapsed bg-danger text-white"
                    type="button"
                    data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                    data-bs-target="#collapseFive"
                    aria-expanded="false"
                    aria-controls="collapseFive"
                  >
                    <h5 class="faqHead">
                      5. When does Lifeline Pay its Tutors?
                    </h5>
                  </button>
                </h2>
                <div
                  id="collapseFive"
                  class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                  data-bs-parent="#accordionExample"
                >
                  <div class="accordion-body">
                    <p>
                      Payment is made not later than the 5th of the preceding
                      month. This is after the tutor has submitted his/her Log
                      Sheet and has been cleared for such.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
